    {"id":"fact.letter-unposted","text":"招聘信仍在信箱中，从未寄出。","immutable":true,"confidence":1,"sourceRefs":[{"sourceId":"source.main","startLine":262,"endLine":284}]},
    {"id":"fact.servants-returned","text":"Mills、Tuttle 与 Lydia 很久以前曾在宅邸工作。","immutable":true,"confidence":1,"sourceRefs":[{"sourceId":"source.main","startLine":288,"endLine":314}]},
    {"id":"fact.victor-seen","text":"Anne 看见 Victor 和参观房子的另一个家庭。","immutable":true,"confidence":1,"sourceRefs":[{"sourceId":"source.main","startLine":529,"endLine":592}]},
